---
Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 4
  Paragraph: 18
Title: In The World Of Men
---
\"You must fast!" said Confucius. "I will tell you what that means. Do
you think it is easy to do anything while you have [a mind]? If you do,
Bright Heaven will not sanction you."
